Package ar.edu.utn.frc.tup.lc.iv.services

Interface CategoryChargeService

All Known Implementing Classes:
CategoryChargeServiceImpl
@Service public interface CategoryChargeService
Service interface for managing Category Charges.

This interface defines the business logic for Category charges operations, including adding, retrieving, and searching Category Charges.
